{"tid":194259,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【IT佬悲歌】中年IT佬：「放工就搵工」","createTime":"2017-04-10T00:07:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T04:02:28.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"064dc2d3f9e50ae8fd26c6f04cc8b1b808f642da","tid":194259,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:07:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/10/080710_cee1ffa89c8551a383969f1a4fe0523f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F10%2F080710_cee1ffa89c8551a383969f1a4fe0523f.jpg&h=6c4bdc08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n滙豐一再引證「裁員一定炒IT先」這一條殘酷的不明文職場定律。身為家中經濟支柱的Samuel（化名）對前景不敢樂觀，合約員工不似早前被裁的長工有一年的「肥雞餐」，一旦失業積蓄只夠捱半年。他坦言，「搵工成為每日其中一個工作，一放工就搵工」。<br />\n<br />\n距離傳聞中的「滙豐千人斬」期限只有半年，可能面對「中年失業」的Samuel亦已打定輸數，預計其他銀行不會請人，轉投其他公司亦難以有相約人工，皆因市場上已未必容得下這批有一定經驗的「中年IT佬」。<br />\n<br />\n「中小企搵唔到人，市場有人但比唔到人工，唔係接受到嘅價錢，見過有公司想用8000蚊請4至5年經驗IT人，低過10年前畢業生價錢。」Samuel指引述市場報告指，約10年經驗的IT人月薪大約4至6萬元，「但未見到有中小企可以出到呢個價錢，有朋友上年11月離職，失業咗半年才搵到新工，仲要減咗唔少人工」。<br />\n<br />\nSamuel於IT行業打滾15年，亦曾赴外國大學進修。被問到有否後悔從事IT業，他仍直言：「冇後悔，花咗十幾年，未來仍會留在IT發展，希望有一日會好轉。」對於到美國或內地發展，他就指「始終香港係自己生長地方，未到最後一刻唔想放棄」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56543733&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170410\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56543733%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170410&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2BynzACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=951f6c66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56543733%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170410&h=635ab5d2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56543733&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170410</a>"},{"pid":"eb02a8283e6e01e9363140cd00d07aaa62d4aab4","tid":194259,"uid":21310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:12:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"273cea6c88bd0e8b57f38164d18750410cbe87fb","tid":194259,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:14:41.000Z","msg":"IT狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b1539b85cb5676aed04eeba2575bae58c027b7c","tid":194259,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:16:46.000Z","msg":"慘無人道，每日收工唔知聽日係咪最後一日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b97b73b8f03d69ce193afd881c4174b173c541","tid":194259,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:18:41.000Z","msg":"睇標題以為係腦魔"},{"pid":"fffb9bc5f17589a2c83ed4ebe0faf3a4b20b11f2","tid":194259,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:26:28.000Z","msg":"又係匯豐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0754ac5f4c1cdedd2a42c80440a2be7cc3f3516","tid":194259,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:31:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係匯豐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n臭極都會有人人入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cd91a5b5754c5a75f8ebf59c134912c7df97bef","tid":194259,"uid":1333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:44:46.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係腦魔開post"},{"pid":"1ec7af3a9c3a0527bf4dc31a13c719f908718875","tid":194259,"uid":34641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:44:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>10年4-6 萬<br />\n我係老細不如2萬請兩個新人入黎好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要10年條友學啲野過晒時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊值4-6萬"},{"pid":"e75a9358679b3e026b41b4c917f8a546265626b9","tid":194259,